{"id":582633,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/04/【立此存照】武汉理工为爸我永远爱你蓝色油/","date":"2018-04-11T09:31:58Z","modified":"2018-04-12T07:27:10Z","title":"【立此存照】武汉理工为“爸我永远爱你”蓝色油漆字洗地","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>当地时间2018年4月10日，有网友在微博曝光称武汉理工大学广场被人用蓝色油漆在地面写上了“是！！！爸我永远爱你！”几个大字，学校相关人员迅速用布盖住了油漆字，并有保洁员用洒水车洗地。爆料微博后被删除。下图为网络流传的蓝色油漆字现场：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_582634\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/爸我永远爱你.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-582634\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/爸我永远爱你.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"669\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">图片来源：新浪微博 @南风北梦yy</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_582579\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/武汉理工大学.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-582579\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/武汉理工大学.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"172\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/武汉理工大学.png 846w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/武汉理工大学-300x103.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/武汉理工大学-768x264.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">被删微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p>4月12日，又有网友在“理工广场马房山通道公交站”见到蓝色油漆字。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/0077u54Yly1fq9vcalgs1j30k00k0gqc.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-582685\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/0077u54Yly1fq9vcalgs1j30k00k0gqc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/0077u54Yly1fq9vcalgs1j30k00k0gqc.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/0077u54Yly1fq9vcalgs1j30k00k0gqc-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/0